S.FORM: DeAndre' Bembry unu syubay kanas mali miunduay nu Amilika NBA nisakaput, u p'agal tins' tay suruw. DeAndre' Bembry i 2016 a mihcan NBA sapapili' mimaliay a kawaw, saka 1 ku uwac atu silsil 21, namapili' tu nu Atlanta Hawks putiput. 7 bulad 4 demiad, 1994 a mihca, DeAndre' Bembry, miunduay. namakayniay a nasulitan nasakamuan atu natinengan Lists of National Basketball Association players
